			       DELETING TEXT
 If you create a document and decide at a later time that the text needs
to be removed, you may do so easily by using Final Copy's "Edit" menu.

 TO DELETE A BLOCK OF TEXT IN THE TUTORIAL DOCUMENT:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. Position the mouse at the first of the blank line that appears above
