appearance of the text in the body of your document by changing the font
size.

 TO CHANGE FONT SIZE:
------------------------------------------------------------------------
 1. Drag the mouse over the line "Professor Sean O'Boyle".

    The text is now selected and ready to have its size changed.

 2. Choose "24" from the "Size" sub-menu of the "Text" menu.

